title: FusionBeauty LipFusion Micro-Injected Collagen Lip Plump Color Shine, Summer
description: A collection of vibrant sexy shades with a moisturizing treatment gloss infused with LipFusion’s revolutionary Micro-Injected Collagen plumping technology.
